    {
        "sha": "c04ebb318d44762495b8f128102215392ba9aadd",
        "author": "Oktawian Chojnacki",
        "email": "oktawian@me.com",
        "date": "2026-03-13T20:19:15Z",
        "message": "Add GitHub Pages support with Jekyll and multilingual language switcher\n\n- Add _config.yml with kramdown, rouge syntax highlighting, and language map\n- Add minimal default layout with language switcher (pure Liquid, no JS)\n- Add YAML front matter to all 12 README files for Jekyll processing\n- Update stylesheet.css with pre/code block styling\n- Update all generator scripts to include front matter in output",
        "url": "https://github.com/ochococo/OOD-Principles-In-Swift/commit/c04ebb318d44762495b8f128102215392ba9aadd"
    },
    {
        "sha": "c364ebc5835afba186764cb887e5388539293481",
        "author": "Oktawian Chojnacki",
        "email": "oktawian@me.com",
        "date": "2026-03-13T16:43:03Z",
        "message": "Add 10 language translations, enhance SOLID descriptions, update social link\n\n- Enhanced all 5 SOLID principle descriptions (EN + KO) with deeper explanations\n  of SRP (actors/stakeholders), OCP (open/closed duality), LSP (behavioral contracts),\n  ISP (client-specific interfaces), DIP (two formal rules)\n- Fixed OCP typo: \"a classes behavior\" → \"a class's behavior\"\n- Added 10 new translations: PL, ZH-CN, PT-BR, JA, ES, UK, DE, FR, HI, TR\n  with source files, generator scripts, playgrounds, and READMEs\n- Updated social link from Twitter to Bluesky across all headers",
        "url": "https://github.com/ochococo/OOD-Principles-In-Swift/commit/c364ebc5835afba186764cb887e5388539293481"
    },
